---
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<section class="relative py-24 overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
  <!-- Background Effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <!-- Radial Glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] animate-pulse-slow"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Grid Pattern -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.15]"
      style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center">
    <div data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1000">
      <h2
        class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight"
      >
        L'excellence médicale <br />
        <span
          class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-300"
          >n'attend pas.</span
        >
      </h2>

      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed">
        Rejoignez les établissements de santé qui ont choisi la fiabilité et la
        performance. Équipez votre structure avec le meilleur du matériel
        médical.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a
          href="/galaxie-medicale/catalog"
          class="group relative inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-8 py-4 bg-white text-slate-900 rounded-full text-lg font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)]"
        >
          <span class="relative z-10">Consulter le catalogue</span>
          <div
            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300"
          >
            <Icon name="heroicons:arrow-right" class="w-4 h-4" />
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Trust Indicators -->
      <div
        class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-8 md:gap-16 opacity-60"
      >
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80">
          <Icon name="heroicons:shield-check" class="w-5 h-5" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">Garantie Constructeur</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/80">
          <Icon name="heroicons:user-group" class="w-5 h-5" />
          <span class="text-sm font-medium">Support Expert</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes pulse-slow {
    0%,
    100% {
      opacity: 0.5;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1);
    }
    50% {
      opacity: 0.8;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.1);
    }
  }
  .animate-pulse-slow {
    animation: pulse-slow 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
</style>
